    <string name="text_help" tools:ignore="MissingTranslation">Tap on the screen to create an obstacle
            pattern. Watch it carefully, remember it!
        \n\nTap to hide the obstacles, and then move the player towards
            the goal. Hit as little obstacles as possible. You can use
            fling gestures to move the player or press and hold on the
            screen to drag it.
        \n\nFor showing the obstacles during the game double-tap on the
            screen. Attention: Turning the device will start a new game.
        \n\nEnjoy!
    </string>
